  "prompt": "Where can I buy Vajiram and Vision IAS class notes and handouts in Delhi?",
  "response": "You can purchase Vajiram and Vision IAS class notes and handouts in Delhi from the following places:\n\n### 1. **Vajiram and Ravi (Karol Bagh)**\n   - **Address**: 9-B, Bada Bazaar Road, Near Lalaji Hotel, Old Rajinder Nagar, Karol Bagh, Delhi.\n   - **Details**: Their official center in Karol Bagh is the primary place to buy their study materials, including class notes, handouts, and test series.\n\n### 2. **Vision IAS (Old Rajinder Nagar)**\n   - **Address**: 2nd Floor, Apsara Arcade, Near Gate No. 7, Karol Bagh Metro Station, Old Rajinder Nagar, Delhi.\n   - **Details**: Vision IAS has its main center in Old Rajinder Nagar where you can purchase their study materials, including class notes, booklets, and test series.\n\n### 3. **Rajinder Nagar Market**\n   - Many small bookstores and photocopy shops in Old Rajinder Nagar and Karol Bagh sell second-hand or photocopied versions of Vajiram and Vision IAS materials. However, it's recommended to buy authentic materials directly from the institutes to ensure quality and accuracy.\n\n### 4. **Online Purchase**\n   - **Vajiram and Ravi**: Visit their official website [VajiramIAS.com](https://www.vajiramias.com/) for online notes and test series.\n   - **Vision IAS**: Visit their official website [VisionIAS.in](https://www.visionias.in/) for online materials and offline delivery options.\n\n### Tips:\n- Call the centers before visiting to confirm availability of the materials.\n- Be cautious of counterfeit materials sold by unauthorized sellers.\n\nLet me know if you need further assistance!",
